  "title": "Purchaser (5 days / Manufacturing)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Support the Purchasing Executive in the full procurement cycle, including order placement, vendor coordination, and inventory management.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and process purchase orders, compile necessary documentation, and liaise with suppliers to ensure timely delivery.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate records of budgets, expenditures, and inventory levels.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to identify cost-saving opportunities and streamline procurement workflows.</li>\n  <li>Perform administrative duties such as data entry, filing, and handling procurement-related inquiries.</li>\n  <li>Assist in developing and implementing purchasing policies and procedures to improve efficiency and ensure compliance.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
